Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川岳？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候和日向一起登的山 那就是谷川岳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時看到的美麗朝陽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法忘記的景色 我想再看一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 和日向一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這麼想的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有纜車啊 我還是不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今你還說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為冷靜的想一想 很可怕啊很高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 和楓談談怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到困難就找楓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐享其成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢 依靠別人也是種才能哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光依靠別人的人少說了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我會發個短信給楓的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 下次我想去登谷川岳 請幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發送
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經回過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可以哦 不過我今天有約了 明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:50.90,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(656,418)}承繼思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:02:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 楓 你今天這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友吵著說讓我打扮的更像女孩子一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是裕香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有點奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常新鮮 很適合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 很像大小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 和高原很配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就去我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 還是第一次去楓家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大山少女 楓的家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會是什麼樣的家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定是像富士山那樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說 昭和新山？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難 難道說是珠穆朗瑪峰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然和想像中不同 但是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天窗 房梁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像海蒂的小屋一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾卑斯的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是個小房間 請隨便坐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 非常大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為今天很熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓 之前縱走的山怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是北阿爾卑斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一個被稱為大巖棱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巖棱？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大山深入低谷的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也被叫做KIRETO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}キレット和キレト只差一个促音 为表区别这里只用罗马音表示 不做汉译
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漢字寫作切處 或者切戶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏你懂的好多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊看啊 我一直都很想去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 超級漂亮 而且非常驚險 可以走到很棒的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小懸崖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有這種踏板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面數百米空無一物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是掉下去就死定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會死的 毫無疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個驚險的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是楓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 楓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從以前就在想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓為什麼不怕那種可怕的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 雖然我想登谷川岳 想要登上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有纜車 果然還是會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵恐高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 無論如何我都想去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓也說過以前很恐高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能告訴我 你是怎麼克服的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊 纜車很可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最開始 通過那個支柱的時候 咚的一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}即將通過支柱 會有晃動 請小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為地板會脫離 抓著桿子嚇得瑟瑟發抖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就發抖可怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我想像了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 坐了兩三次以後 已經習慣 什麼感覺都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩三次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 就算害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要習慣了就會意外地覺得沒什麼了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己一直認為可怕 感到不安 其實也沒什麼了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼了不起的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 比如說登山 去的時候可怕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去的時候卻不怎麼可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵也有經驗的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前在三增卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個懸崖 回去的時候也沒那麼可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定是覺得可怕的自己的心 讓自己更加害怕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的心…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下定決心就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就只能去了 自然就會做出覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得危險的話 隨時都可以撤回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煩惱的話 總之先向前進如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案隨後就會出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要邁出步伐 或許根本就不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓足勇氣向前邁出腳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 心夏 楓 暑假我們去谷川岳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然OK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於要去登谷川岳了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走到這一步走了好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 為什麼要去谷川岳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前楓推薦過的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有… 其實我小時候和日向登過那座山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 回憶中的谷川岳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的那麼了不起 日向連是哪裏的山都不記得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是小學的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我恐高之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了非常美麗的朝陽的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要再去一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那就要住山中小屋了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我去預約一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過能不能看到朝陽就要看運氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好像是雨女…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是晴天就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到天氣我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝備和富士山那時的一樣就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家有雨衣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有 之前用存下的打工費買了件貴的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯吧 啊 會不會下雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是下雨就看不到朝陽了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒事 雖然有點舊 媽媽以前給我做了一件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 葵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然以前覺得需要買查過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻相當貴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 你身高多少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,152cm
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要用我的舊雨衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中學時候買的 已經穿不上了 送給葵了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在發愁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是和朋友一起挑選的衣服 不想扔掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵能用的話我會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真幸運呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 穿上試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很適合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很配你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點破 將就一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會努力制定計劃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼對我是這種反應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在給你加油嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不讓日向笑話我 要好好制定計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到有登山電梯的天神平要坐大約7分鐘的纜車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出勇氣 向前邁出一步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為前進的方向 一定有美麗的景色在等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未完待續
